 these nanofabricated slits to the machined\nslits with on-sky data, in addition to making the etched slits more robust\nagainst breakage and finalizing the slit manufacturing process.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Feb 2023 19:58:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-20"}
