en in the framework. Extending the\nvalidity of the Equivalence Principle to the quantum level, the quantum frame\nfields theory at low energy gives an effective theory of gravity, a scale\ndependent Einstein-Hilbert action plus a cosmological constant is recovered. As\na possible underlying microscopic theory of gravity, the theory is also applied\nto understand the thermodynamics of the Schwarzschild black hole.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Feb 2023 01:53:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-20"}
