dingly diminishing of the\ninner peaks in the turbulence production profiles. The skewness and flatness\nprofiles show that the zero skewness and minimum flatness locations of the\nstreamwise and wall-normal velocity fluctuations collapse with the location of\nthe maximum Reynolds streamwise stress in the TBLs irrespective of the pressure\ngradient imposed on the TBL.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Feb 2023 06:04:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-20"}
