acy and good earthquake detection performance. We then apply\nthe model to process continuous data and build earthquake catalogs directly\nfrom DAS recording. Our approach using semi-supervised learning provides a way\nto build effective deep learning models for DAS, which have the potential to\nimprove earthquake monitoring using large-scale fiber networks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Feb 2023 08:16:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Mar 2023 19:15:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-16"}
