se). At distances much larger than the light cylinder, the\nresulting shear Alfven waves propagate through the wind non-dissipatively.\nImplications to Fast Radio Bursts are discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Feb 2023 12:43:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-20"}
